      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Iterative convergence was monitored during simulations and residuals were observed to drop below 1e-5 for all equations, but formal solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring was not performed. This is acceptable for the required level at MRL 2."
    },
