      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. The SST k-omega turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model were selected based on literature precedent for blood pump CFD. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification was not performed, consistent with MRL 2 scope."
    },
    {
