      "acceptanceCriteria": "Characterization of test sample variability and its effect on validation conclusions must be documented.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. A single pump prototype was used for in-vitro testing. Pump-to-pump manufacturing variability was not characterized. This limitation is acknowledged; the assessment is considered acceptable. No documentation is provided explaining why sample-to-sample variability does not affect the credibility conclusion for the COU."
